code: @Override public IngestDocument execute(IngestDocument ingestDocument) throws Exception {     ingestDocument.appendFieldValue(field, value).     return ingestDocument. }

@Override public AppendProcessor create(Map<String, Processor.Factory> registry, String processorTag, Map<String, Object> config) throws Exception {     String field = ConfigurationUtils.readStringProperty(TYPE, processorTag, config, "field").     Object value = ConfigurationUtils.readObject(TYPE, processorTag, config, "value").     TemplateScript.Factory compiledTemplate = ConfigurationUtils.compileTemplate(TYPE, processorTag, "field", field, scriptService).     return new AppendProcessor(processorTag, compiledTemplate, ValueSource.wrap(value, scriptService)). }
